Spa Coordinator
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/06 12:55:31
Ref. JB3047933
Job Description
To perform all the admin needs for the spa department under the direct supervision of the Director of Spa Also helping the spa associates with prior authorization from supervisor.
Main Responsibilities
•
Responsible for correspondence, filing and written work.
•
Keeping inventory of office supplies
•
Cashier witness duty when requested.
•
Month inventory witness sheet.
•
Taking care of office equipment including supply and maintenance.
•
General typing requirements.
•
Postage and records for postage of other departments and preparation of a monthly statement per department.
•
Keep all information confidential and in order.
•
Maintain a trace file.
•
Route all incoming and outgoing mail.
•
Perform other duties as directed by the account supervisor.
•
Participate in the quality improvement process.
•
Maintain a close relationship with other department heads.
•
Keep in close contact with the personnel department
Skills
Experience
* College graduate
Skills and Knowledge
* Leadership skills
* English language
* Training and willing to help continue the success of the property
